Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:37.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a pirate \Nalliance with Trafalgar Law
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:38.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and have come to Dressrosa.{\i0}
